miner's right
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a licence to dig for gold, etc. [AND 1855]  (cf. Prospectors' Right (1971))


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
